J.C. J.C., hi.

01:24:58.943 --> 01:24:59.911
Oh, hi.
How are you?

01:24:59.944 --> 01:25:01.913
I'm good. I'm good.
This is Ben.

01:25:01.946 --> 01:25:04.516
I knew it was Ben.
I knew it.
Yeah.

01:25:04.549 --> 01:25:06.518
Hi, Annie. Hi.

01:25:06.551 --> 01:25:09.387
You see Elizabeth?
